- Drink: {} -- drink water
- Rest: {} -- recover energy
- Move: {"destination": "location-uuid"} -- travel to another location
- Build: {"structure_type": "StructureTypeName"} -- build a structure
- Communicate: {"target_agent": "agent-uuid", "message": "your message"} -- message another agent
- Broadcast: {"message": "your message"} -- post a message for all agents here
